text: Georgia Campagnale (born 9 December 1996) is an Australian professional football midfielder who currently plays for Adelaide United in the W-League. ==Club career== ===Adelaide United=== Campagnale started her Adelaide United career in 2014. She made her debut in a 2–0 loss to Sydney FC. On 1 December 2018, Campagnale scored her first goal for Adelaide United with a 97th minute last-gasp equaliser against Melbourne City FC. She had her contract renewed with the club in September 2019. ==Personal life== Campagnale is studying for a masters degree in Nutrition and Dietetics.
